h - HTTPie Client

USAGE:
    h [-request=method] [-q|--quiet] [--no-log-env] [-s=host] [--session=name]

DESCRIPTION:
    HTTPie command-line HTTP client with various options.

OPTIONS:
    -request=method
        HTTP request method

    -q|--quiet
        Quiet mode

    --no-log-env
        Don't log environment variables

    -s=host
        Server host

    --session=name
        Session name

EXAMPLES:
    h -request=GET
    h -q --session=myapp
    h -s=api.example.com --no-log-env
